included.description: In this UX Researcher role, I focused my attention on text entry methods for the 2015 SmartTV platform. I worked closely with senior researchers and engineers to determine the positive and negatives of entry methods in order to create a better core user experience for search and exploration. Here, I moderated over 10 usability sessions, and gathered qualitative and quantitative data to present to the design team and others at HQ.
